Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:40.59,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H74A5FA&}天王星行星力量 变身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:17:00.82,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H96BB00&}深海淹没
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.07,0:17:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能把这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒车 倒车
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来吧 戴蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴蒙？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在搞什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋装太重了 行动有点困难…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:42.56,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}午夜12点的钟声还没响起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:44.77,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}就想提前离开的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.75,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFDC228&}就不是灰姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:49.49,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2626FF&}你这个制造麻烦的冒牌货
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:51.58,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H37DB00&}不管是睡美人中的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:53.77,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H37DB00&}还是天鹅湖中的魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:57.39,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H37DB00&}这些坏人最后终将被打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:18:01.42,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C71FD&}辛蒂蕾拉与睡美人跟奥杰塔公主还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:02.86,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}我们要代表他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:05.59,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}来惩罚你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头痛的东西又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是魔具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 你又白跑一趟了 尤嘉露
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的预感果然对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留声机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样 剩下的交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留声机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One Two Three
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.97,0:18:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One Two Three
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水手月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留声机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.61,0:18:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看不下去了
