Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天王星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.98,0:19:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我多此一举了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留声机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还没被打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是顽固的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留声机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱的华尔兹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 竟然把音符丢出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样是作弊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留声机就应该像留声机一样 用音乐来决胜负啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意见还真是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我放刚完成的新曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔的小山歌 山歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难听
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:20:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这首歌会刺激人的中枢系统
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐是让人来享受的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是用来折磨人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕尾服假面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,践踏美丽音乐的人 我是不会原谅他的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在 水手月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:54.82,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}月亮螺旋心 攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.16,0:21:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道这样我就不扔掉喇叭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lovely
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.31,0:21:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才是不是睡着了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 我没有注意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好幸福的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 小遥呢 我要找她跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.10,0:21:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 石头剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信玫瑰色的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把希望寄托在下一代身上 原来也可以这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我们已经快没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉默已经逼近了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.22,0:21:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了防止这件事情发生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须要快点找到魔具
